      <scopecontent id="aspace_ec81e2f6196c6c00ef0640165843cfd9">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>This collection documents the American pianist, singer and actor, Liberace, largely between the 1950s and 1980s. Material includes photographs, printed material, scripts, posters, phonograph records, and ephemera relating to Liberace and his career.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_1e9ac7e631b2f1a9f8da2e11c3a8338f">
